---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services — NexTara AI Solutions"
  description="Governed digital growth systems: DCS audits, tracking governance, conversion architecture, and automation."
>
  <main data-nt-section="services">
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container page-pad-top">
        <p class="nt-eyebrow">Services</p>
        <h1>Governed Digital Growth Systems</h1>
        <p>
          We build and govern the digital system behind your business—so performance is measurable,
          credibility is defensible, and growth is controllable.
        </p>

        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/dcs-diagnostic/" data-nt-event="services_cta_diagnostic">
            Run Your DCS Score
          </a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/contact/" data-nt-event="services_cta_contact">
            Request a Consultation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="nt-grid">
          <article class="nt-card">
            <h2>DCS Audits (PromptCore)</h2>
            <p>Compliance-grade technical credibility verification with prioritized remediation.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="nt-card">
            <h2>Tracking Governance</h2>
            <p>GTM-only instrumentation, clean analytics, event hygiene, and proof-based reporting.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="nt-card">
            <h2>Conversion Architecture</h2>
            <p>Funnels, forms, thank-you endpoints, and measurable actions tied to business outcomes.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="nt-card">
            <h2>SEO + Indexing Systems</h2>
            <p>Sitemaps, internal linking, crawl policy, structured data, and search visibility control.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="nt-card">
            <h2>Automation (ECC)</h2>
            <p>Operational automations that reduce manual work and eliminate reporting ambiguity.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="nt-card">
            <h2>Paid Media Systems</h2>
            <p>Campaign structure + measurement discipline so spend is governed, not guessed.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="nt-cta-card">
          <h2>Start with proof.</h2>
          <p>Run your DCS Score and we’ll tell you what’s real, what’s missing, and what to fix first.</p>
          <div class="cta-row">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/dcs-diagnostic/" data-nt-event="services_cta_bottom_diagnostic">
              Run Your DCS Score
            </a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/contact/" data-nt-event="services_cta_bottom_contact">
              Talk to NexTara
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
